quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  102,1,Fierce competition for this world distracted you
  102,2,until you went down to the graves
  102,3,"No indeed, you will soon know"
  102,4,"Again no indeed, you will soon know"
  102,5,"No indeed, if you only knew with the Knowledge of Certainty"
  102,6,you will certainly see the Blazing Fire
  102,7,Then you will certainly see it with the Eye of Certainty
  102,8,Then you will be asked that Day about the pleasures you enjoyed